            "type": "text/vnd.tiddlywiki",
            "text": "I'm trying to follow the rules of [[Semantic Versioning|https://semver.org/]].

!! 1.1.2

[[See GitLab for detailed change history of this release|https://gitlab.com/bimlas/tw5-disqus/compare/v1.0.0...v1.1.2]]

* [[Added|https://gitlab.com/bimlas/tw5-disqus/merge_requests/2]] toolbar button for jumping to Disqus comments
* [[Fixed|https://gitlab.com/bimlas/tw5-disqus/merge_requests/1]] generation of static pages
* [[Changed|https://gitlab.com/bimlas/tw5-disqus/commit/324be06048616b6753729d0607b0fd7c7c6b6c4f]] Disqus icon to SVG format

!! 1.0.0

* First public release
"
